No. 09-658. Brian Belleque, Superintendent, Oregon State Penitentiary, Petitioner v. Randy Joseph Moore. 559 U.S. 1004, 130 S. Ct. 1882,

176 L. Ed. 2d 361,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2679. March 22, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted.

Same case below, 574 F.3d 1092.
